        - Less false positives for pep3101.
          [do3cc]
        
        - Add ``--jobs=1`` to flake8 if ``multiprocessing`` is set to ``False``.
          [saily]
        
        - Fix #151 by not instantiating ``Lock`` and ``Value`` if ``multiprocessing``
          was set to ``False``.
          [saily]
        
        
